{"text": "## Seek medical attention as soon as possible if:\n\n\nThere is a foreign object (soil, wood, metal, or other objects) embedded in the wound;\n\nA wound is a result of an animal bite;\n\nA wound is a result of a puncture by a dirty object;\n\nThe wound is infected (pain and soreness, swelling, redness, draining, or you develop a fever);\n\nYou have signs of sepsis such as confusion or disorientation, shortness of breath, high heart rate, fever or shivering, extreme pain or discomfort or clammy or sweaty skin.\n\nIf you have wounds, you should be evaluated for a tetanus immunization. If you receive a puncture wound or a wound contaminated with feces, soil, or saliva, have a health care professional determine whether a tetanus booster is necessary based on individual records.\n\nCS 283563", "embedding": [0.06736541, 0.030908583, -0.17161883, -0.044037372, 0.08069233, 0.017822536, -0.0032530176, 0.028280552, 0.08448318, -0.08480954, 0.0019142679, 0.029403854, 0.03947892, 0.008581633, 0.014927897, -0.07754805, -0.00063759345, -0.036527567, 0.0038226591, 0.026021238, -0.058991645, -0.010169822, -0.016966525, -0.010689478, 0.021841832, 0.014694307, -0.020317199, 0.08785018, -0.0057426402, 0.005401736, 0.04928048, -0.015152074, 0.0065460415, 0.0012978275, -0.04672683, -0.047677167, 0.035488777, 0.04004475, 0.012969584, 0.018887237, 0.04860592, -0.017601207, 0.03394063, -0.074354276, 0.010664214, 0.018251307, 0.05359168, 0.043951854, 0.07312483, -0.033248596, 0.0023738635, -0.09193332, -0.03691684, -0.054834045, 0.059545413, -0.0019498168, 0.03176714, -0.054571316, 0.047267325, -0.00057711697, 0.08052433, 0.07075649, -0.07672061, 0.009893535, 0.03682579, -0.024486579, -0.060754128, 0.0602446, 0.017976098, 0.029864386, 0.036319572, 0.017374946, 0.020431342, 0.021448012, -0.03550281, 0.017192457, -0.025389018, 0.0010233487, -0.01961595, 0.0035903975, 0.024335885, -0.013491161, 0.056871593, -0.03524424, 0.03683268, -0.049266577, -0.05649279, -0.017469388, -0.01098833